title: Curb Appeal: The Johannes Mueller House of Lititz
text:
Buy Now DAN MARSCHKA | Staff Photographer 
The Mueller house dates to the mid-18th century, and is the oldest home still in existence in Lititz. Buy Now DAN MARSCHKA | Staff Photographer 
The Mueller backyard on East Main Street in Lititz, where farm animals were housed. A trough is repurposed as a flower box.
